title: The Packet Passer 4.0
description:
In 2009, My software program called "The Packet Passer 4.0" was sponsored by members of the Intel Corporation. Over the years I have won several awards for this software and now I am offering it FREE online.


Packets contain personal information such as usernames,passwords,credit card information, etc... and can slow down your computer. The Packet Passer 4.0 scrambles the packets you do have and deletes the old unused ones to help keep your personal information safe. I also helps keep your internet connection at a constant speed and lag free.
